section.section:
The Board:
May establish the license fee;
Shall choose a location in the county for this Festival which is not licensed under this article;
Shall assure that the primary focus of the Festival is the promotion of Maryland wine; and
Subject to paragraph (2) of this subsection, annually may select one weekend, Friday through Sunday inclusive, for the Festival.

The weekend chosen for the Festival may not:
Be longer than 3 days;
Occur within 14 days before or after the Maryland Wine Festival in Carroll County; and
Conflict with the dates chosen for:
The Anne Arundel County Beer and Wine Festival;
The Calvert County Wine Festival;
The Charles County Beer and Wine Festival; or
The Howard County Wine Festival.
